                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-2-defend65 t18180506-2-punish11"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 50.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron Garrow.</p>
